    section.section-about(style="background: #636363 url(../img/about-background.png);")
      .container
        .about-wrapper
          .about-text
            h3 About ignite
            p ignite is a healthcare growth agency that specialises in attracting high-value patients.
            p Whether you’re an orthodontist, plastic surgeon, facial aesthetician or implant dentist, we know how to get you patients. We work with practices that are tired of waiting for referrals or word of mouth to grow their practice.
            a(href="#").button.button-white LEARN MORE

